dcterms:description: DSTC2 is the traditional standard dialog state tracking benchmark on a single restaurant domain, where the dialog system interacts with a user who wants to find a specified restaurant around Cambridge, UK.
dcterms:title: DSTC2

dcterms:description: MultiWOZ 2.1 is the latest corrected version of the MultiWOZ dataset, containing around 10K dialogues with multiple domains and a variety of slots and slot values.
dcterms:title: MultiWOZ 2.1

dcterms:description: Modified MultiWOZ 2.1 is a dataset derived from MultiWOZ 2.1, created to evaluate the ability of models to extract unknown slot values containing multiple out-of-vocabulary words.
dcterms:title: Modified MultiWOZ 2.1
